@startuml UC22_Sequence
title UC22: 备份系统数据 - 顺序图

actor "管理员" as Admin
boundary "备份触发页面" as BackupPage
control "维护控制器" as MaintCtrl
entity "DataArchive" as Archive
entity "BackupLog" as Log

Admin -> BackupPage : 触发手动备份
BackupPage -> MaintCtrl : initiateBackup()
MaintCtrl -> Archive : performHotBackup()
Archive --> MaintCtrl : backupFileRef
MaintCtrl -> Log : createEntry(ref)
MaintCtrl --> BackupPage : 备份成功及文件下载链接
@enduml
